==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dreamland
<hw>Dream"land`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An unreal,
delightful country such as in sometimes pictured in dreams; region of
fancies; fairyland.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>[He] builds a bridge from <qex>dreamland</qex> for his lay.</q>
<rj><qau>Lowell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dreamless</ent>⟦br⟧
